Felix | D1strict Apr 17, 2022 @ 9:57
Hello,

I think this one is wrong:

## get IPv4 ##
$ host myip.opendns.com resolver1.opendns.com
And should probably be as follows:

## get IPv4 ##
$ host -4 myip.opendns.com resolver1.opendns.com
Greetings,
Felix

